{"id": 2971, "genre": 1001, "title": "对一个成年人来说，你觉得哪些“关心”过头了？", "description": "打着关心的幌子八卦和嘲讽，听着让人不适感翻倍。（图片来源：istock ©️ nuvolanevicata）", "record_count": 1636, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190527152520UTEhnsRmGtzcAYIH.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-09-03T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 346381, "content": "海底捞。\n与我有关但与你无关的个人生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802061}, {"id": 346127, "content": "我是艺考生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660140}, {"id": 348181, "content": "不熟的人，问什么都很烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 218568}, {"id": 346394, "content": "你怎么又不吃饭 又减肥   怎么吃这么少  是不是怕胖？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532535}, {"id": 346142, "content": "你这个发际线有点高嘛 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1658154}, {"id": 346145, "content": "打探个人情况，已经不愿意说了，还是刨根问底", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1214137}, {"id": 346147, "content": "该找对象了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440051}, {"id": 346148, "content": "让一切发生都显得自然，一切都算不过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446219}, {"id": 346149, "content": "你现在一个月能开上4000吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660242}, {"id": 346150, "content": "别再关心我在学习什么了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1659638}, {"id": 346151, "content": "你咋不穿胸罩？", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660256}, {"id": 346152, "content": "被不喜欢的人骚扰", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1659864}, {"id": 346153, "content": "替我孤单", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114719}, {"id": 346161, "content": "没来由的关心即是负担", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112973}, {"id": 346162, "content": "什么时候结婚?什么时候生孩子？", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427249}, {"id": 346163, "content": "你眼镜几度了呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244859}, {"id": 346164, "content": "你钱花得完嘛？花不完我帮你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1658943}, {"id": 346167, "content": "长辈频繁送些他们审美的服饰给我。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1654358}, {"id": 346168, "content": "有时候商店里紧跟的导购和每天都要提醒几次有小🐥来偷吃的app红点点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633409}, {"id": 346169, "content": "现代不过是知不可言，言不可尽。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1659735}, {"id": 346170, "content": "你怎么不合群啊？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660378}, {"id": 346171, "content": "以自己为是的关心来体现对你的高人一等", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346662}, {"id": 346177, "content": "你背上包准备去哪？要干什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524378}, {"id": 346689, "content": "你应该这样做 不应该这么做！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1638120}, {"id": 346434, "content": "交浅言深", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661580}, {"id": 346183, "content": "我还能怎么办，都在为我操心，你多高 .190.打篮球吗?.不打.这大高个不打篮球可惜了。这是我人生最致命的问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412144}, {"id": 346184, "content": "所有不喜欢的人的关心都是过头了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660552}, {"id": 346952, "content": "关注私生活 并“贴心”告诉我该如何如何做", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662980}, {"id": 346185, "content": "你毕业之后干嘛去，能做什么工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660563}, {"id": 346186, "content": "如果是身边的人问我，我基本都乐于回答，从未有关心过头这种概念。可能是太怕孤独了。我可能会成为过于关心别人的那个。因为我不喜欢一直和我在一起的人莫名其妙的消失，那会很可怕。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660597}, {"id": 346188, "content": "问啥我都不高兴😫", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 842623}, {"id": 346189, "content": "你这耳机...得好几百吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455533}, {"id": 346191, "content": "没必要，对于不熟的人说啥都是多余的，可以问个路", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660682}, {"id": 346447, "content": "不是很熟的阿姨莫名其妙地给你介绍男朋友还在未经本人允许的情况下将你的照片发她朋友圈，发了之后还很自得，微信截图朋友圈还私发给你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661874}, {"id": 346192, "content": "是不是你爸妈离婚了你就不认你爸爸了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1468596}, {"id": 346193, "content": "太晚了，快睡吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274409}, {"id": 346964, "content": "无权发言，我就是关心过头了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662559}, {"id": 346202, "content": "跟你没有任何关系的所有事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1592706}, {"id": 346207, "content": "读QS世界排名前50的大学能学到什么？考得上公务员吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 860967}, {"id": 346208, "content": "问薪水", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001727}, {"id": 346209, "content": "总认为我写小说就是有心理疾病", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316757}, {"id": 346210, "content": "有事没事总是来打扰我的生活，说是怕我孤独，其实只是她自己孤独。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661020}, {"id": 345704, "content": "在别人拍的照片底下评论：“这样穿冷不冷／这样穿不怕热吗”", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 345709, "content": "不怎么熟的人跑过来聊天东拉西扯打探你的近况", "image": null, "praise_count": 299, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 345710, "content": "“有男朋友了还化妆干嘛呀容易让对方误会”", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 346738, "content": "个人隐私", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1658884}, {"id": 348278, "content": "吃了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666397}, {"id": 346238, "content": "都23了，还不谈恋爱？改天我给你介绍一个，见个面了解一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661048}, {"id": 346239, "content": "话太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1533804}, {"id": 346241, "content": "出去玩要玩的开心一点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1658144}]}